<html>
  <head>
    <title>Are.na + Slack: Help</title>
    <%= partial 'public/partials/_head.html.erb' %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class='icon'>
      <a href='/'><img src='img/icon.png'></a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h1>Are.na + Slack: Help</h1>
    </p>
    <p>
      This bot posts channel updates from Are.na to Slack.
    </p>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>
      Invite <b>@arena</b> to a channel.
      <br><small><em>/invite @arena</em></small>
    </p>
    <p>
      Search for a channel or user with <b>/arena search [text]</b>.<br>
      Click on the interactive <b>Connect</b> and <b>Follow</b> buttons.<br>
      <small>eg. <em>/arena search david</em></small>
    </p>
    <p>
      See all connected feeds with <b>/arena feeds</b>.<br>
      See all channels with <b>/arena channels</b> and users with <b>/arena users</b>.<br>
      Click on the interactive <b>Disconnect</b> and <b>Unfollow</b> buttons.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you know a channel URL, connect it with <b>/arena connect [channel]</b>.
      <br><small>eg. <em>/arena connect delightfully-absurd</em></small>
      <br>If you know a user URL, follow them with <b>/arena follow [user]</b>.
      <br><small>eg. <em>/arena follow charles-broskoski</em></small>
    </p>
    <p>
      If you know a channel URL, disconnect it with <b>/arena disconnect [channel]</b>.
      <br><small>eg. <em>/arena disconnect delightfully-absurd</em></small>
      <Br>If you know a user URL, unfollow them with <b>/arena unfollow [user]</b>.
      <br><small>eg. <em>/arena unfollow charles-broskoski</em></small>
    </p>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <%= partial 'public/partials/_footer.html.erb' %>
  </body>
</html>

